text: The Bachelor's Daughters is a 1946 American comedy movie directed by Andrew L. Stone and starring Gail Russell, Ann Dvorak, Claire Trevor, Adolphe Menjou, Billie Burke, Jane Wyatt, Damian O'Flynn, Eugene List, Russell Hicks. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * Category:1946 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Andrew L. Stone
title: The Bachelor's Daughters
